Update the Exchange Rate
Setup --> Company Information --> Currency Setup --> Edit Rates --> Euro to 1.00 --> Save 
==========================================================================================================================================================================
You can check the difference if you want
App Launcher --> Sales --> Opportunities --> Euro Currency Test
